    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and runs like a dream! Whether you\u2019re heading to work or planning a road trip, this car is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll feel the love the moment you hop in for a test drive. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
