    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile shifts, while the M Variable Differential Lock provides superior power delivery through the apex. Recent service includes a cooling system refresh and the installation of Bilstein B12 dampers for enhanced dampening characteristics without sacrificing streetability. The exterior retains its factory depth with minor road-going patina, and the interior remains a functional, driver-centric environment. A turn-key example for the purist seeking a balanced, high-performance longitudinal layout.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34500.0,
