    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and totally ready for its next big adventure. It runs like a dream and has been a joy to own, but it's time for it to find a new home. It\u2019s clean, dependable, and honestly just a blast to drive. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
