    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing linear power delivery to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, the drivetrain offers pure mechanical engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral loads. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for performance and longevity.",
